<p>Several of my long-running open loops wrapped up in the last few days in a combination of personal milestones and external results. It feels great closing off all these background processes and resolving uncertainties. Looking back, I don&#8217;t remember all that much hard work. More like kicking things off, then being patient for a while. [&#8230;]</p>
